		,"154Sm - 0.29 %."
		,"Back-to-back 148Sm samples were placed at the common"
		,"cathode of the ionization chamber."
		,". 238U(3)O(8) sample to measure the absolute neutron"
		,"flux by detecting of fission fragments."
		," Abundance 99.999 %, thickness 0.475 mg/cm2,"
		,"diameter 44.0 mm."]
